text: haey( chaur changcha) nowpel del ai pr hi m ban buongsuong som tha ao mcheasa robsakhnhom. saum trong me tda thveu aoy tukdei nih( krong mea kkah) chea kanleng muoy del mean sovotthephap promteang phdal phleanouphl krob braphet dl brachachn now tinih del mean chomnue leu a l laoh ning thngai barlok knongchamnaom puokke phng choh . trong ban mean bantoul tb vinh tha champoh anak del kmean chomnue yeung nung touk aokasa aoy ke sabbayrikreay te muoyorypel khlei bonnaoh . banteabmk yeung bangkham anak noh aoy towkean tearounakamm nei phleung nork del chea kanleng vil tralb da akrak cheatibamphot
